{"tid":1349413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義士勿灰心，某程度我覺得今日焦點係元朗件事係好事","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T10:26:05.000Z","uid":4780,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"995100e11605197bc0a4c283a61df04f5c9487a3","tid":1349413,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"純粹我覺得，假如尋晚無發生元朗事件，今日既輿論就一定會講緊義士圍中聯辦，掟漆彈掟磚，咁又係會令我地繼續不停文宣戰去反攻。<br />\n<br />\n但相反發生尋晚既事，好多人特別一直扮訓既人都睇到，黑警到底有幾咁丟架，警黑到底係點樣勾結到上台面。而且更加令所有聲音都譴責緊黑警同政府，我認為咁樣對我地更加有利，對下次既行動更加出師有名！<br />\n<br />\n辛苦晒前線既義士，你地食既彈一定唔會白食！ 加油！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"cff57f180b70f9a27192c527e7e9d3b380496ee2","tid":1349413,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:24:15.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰今日繼續提供義載 睇下有冇巴打需要<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/doeigT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/doeigT</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f620d465695df21f1bd6903ad3cffc114f9af5","tid":1349413,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}